    "description": "The life of a mad scientist's servant is not a bad one, but when an angry mob shows up life gets a lot more complicated.<br />\r\nCan you keep the mob at bay, escape the mob, and save our hapless hero from their wrath?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\nA classic humorous 2D Point and Click adventure game, reminiscent of the classic Lucas-arts and Sierra games, all in a hand drawn silent movie inspired visual aesthetic.<br />\r\nInteract with a full cast of amusing characters, combine items in unlikely ways, and of course commit minor acts of larceny in order to escape to freedom! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nA mixture of inventory, dialogue and character puzzles handled through a simple contextual verb coin.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBuilt up from the original (winning) entry of the $105 Adventure Game Challenge in 2021.",
